    "companyDescription": "<p>At the high-level, the areas we want the students to gain experience are -</p><p>1) Improving and updating the company web site</p><p>2) iOS programming (Objective C and/or Swift) to enhance existing mobile apps.</p><p>3) AI algorithms for person identification using face &amp; voice data.</p><p>4) Blockchain integration to transmit and/or receive tokens from biometric data</p><p>5) Creating fintech apps with biometrics</p><p>6) Integrating Apple Cloudkit framework to simple app database</p><p>7) Prototyping active-RFID receiver/transmitter for 20-100 feet range</p><p>8) Miniaturizing the prototype in 7</p><p>9) Cost optimization of the prototype in 8</p><p>Progress, goals, achievements can be self-paced in a reasonable manner.</p><p>The company encourages passionate, motivated students to consistently &amp;</p><p>persistently work on exciting problems of real-life, business oriented issues.</p><p>Groups 2-3 per problem will generate cross-creativity, mutual learning while making</p><p>it fun.</p><p>Students will learn &amp; retain a whole set of technical &amp; business experience which can</p><p>take them to higher &amp; higher peaks in their journey of Enterprenur ship and</p><p>Creativity.</p>",
